            "p": [
                "Situated in beautiful Golden British-Columbia at the foot of the Kicking-Horse River. Our shop is located in one of Golden's very few heritage buildings. The Golden mountain bike scene has grown exponentially in the past few years with over 100 km of single-track. The Golden Cycling Club is 400 members strong. Come in and see us for directions, trails conditions and a trail maps. "
